imdb.plot outline: Lee Gwang Jae is a rich boy that inherits a huge amount of debt and struggles to pay it back to save his father's reputation. By his side is Kim Young Ha, a dauntless girl who fully supports him. is a TV series that shows that this world is worth living as long as you have the courage and true love, through an immature rich kid and an innocent girl that struggle to make money, starting from the bottom.
